        <abstract> 
<p>Illness has prevented his reading <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. He has, however, expressed his [negative] opinion on the subject of mutability of species in his <hi rend="italic">Manual of geology</hi> [1862]. Since his persuasions are so strong, he can do no less.</p> 
        </abstract>
